      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. While it currently runs, the engine has a noticeable knock, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. The body has extensive rust, several large dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. This would be an ideal project car for someone looking to do a full restoration or a valuable source of parts.",
