    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and flawless mechanical performance, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine exterior finish to the original, untouched interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. Experience unrivaled prestige in a vehicle that remains indistinguishable from its initial delivery state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
